I am marking EVERY Elite quest and dungeons as optional in this guide. Especially on release you should do them!!! You'll easily find groups for elite quests and dungeons.
Kill Coldarra Spellbinders until you loot a Scintillating Fragment. Thats a questItem. Accept it.
Text: Kill Coldarra Spellbinders until you loot a Scintillating Fragment. Thats a questItem. Accept it.

Name: Use the questItem you just got.
Text: Use the questItem you just got.

Name: Talk to Keristrasza and say that you're ready to face Saragosa. Use your Arcane Power Focus and kill the now weakened Saragosa.
Text: Talk to Keristrasza and say that you're ready to face Saragosa. Use your Arcane Power Focus and kill the now weakened Saragosa.

Name: Use the questItem again and get teleported to Transitus Shield.
Text: Use the questItem again and get teleported to Transitus Shield.

Name: Kill Coldarra Wyrmkins for 5 Frozen Axes.
Text: Kill Coldarra Wyrmkins for 5 Frozen Axes.

Name: You got all Nexus-Dungeon quests now. I will NOT list them here as part of the guide. Do them as you please.
